    "description": "Freeland is a virtual universe waiting to be explored, conquered, and shaped by your choices in this VR role-playing adventure. Immerse yourself in a colossal galactic online adventure where expansive open worlds teem with endless possibilities. Engage in quests that will challenge and reward you as you traverse this ever-evolving virtual universe. Unveil the rich storyline and forge your identity while connecting with players from across the globe through unparalleled social experiences.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705390/extras/78a8a22e1441f5218a5af71f8a39407e.poster.avif?t=1752211073\" width=590 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705390/extras/78a8a22e1441f5218a5af71f8a39407e.webm?t=1752211073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705390/extras/78a8a22e1441f5218a5af71f8a39407e.mp4?t=1752211073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The galaxy is on the brink of destruction, and Ventax, the rogue all-powerful architect, threatens the very fabric of existence. Your mission is clear: to travel across multiple planets, forge alliances, and bring peace to the people of Freeland. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705390/extras/0bd7f183606744dd888ffde9f9f4fbfa.poster.avif?t=1752211073\" width=638 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705390/extras/0bd7f183606744dd888ffde9f9f4fbfa.webm?t=1752211073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705390/extras/0bd7f183606744dd888ffde9f9f4fbfa.mp4?t=1752211073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>●Create your unique virtual identity.<br><br>●Forge alliances and make friends as you meet other players in the online universe.<br><br>●Explore diverse open-world planets and become immersed in the virtual galaxy.<br><br>●Find or craft gear and upgrade your skills, with magic and weaponry.<br><br>●Engage in immersive quests and help save the Freeland Galaxy from Ventax.<br><br>●Travel freely between planets with your spaceship.<br><br>●Fight in epic battles against Ventax’s armies spread across the planets.<br><br>●Race to the top of the leaderboards with cars, spaceships, jet skis, mounts and parkour races.<br><br>●Challenge other players in arena battles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705390/extras/735db95e7e58b0346b0a963e24967b3d.poster.avif?t=1752211073\" width=558 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705390/extras/735db95e7e58b0346b0a963e24967b3d.webm?t=1752211073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705390/extras/735db95e7e58b0346b0a963e24967b3d.mp4?t=1752211073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Enter the Freeland universe and join the epic adventure! Are you ready for the future of VR Gaming? Dive into Freeland now!",
